tiers.ability_description: Dark Side allies recover 2% Health whenever they critically hit an enemy.
Whenever a debuff on an enemy expires, Clone Trooper allies gain 2% Turn Meter, doubled if that debuff was dispelled by an enemy.
The first time each Light Side ally reaches 75%, 50%, and 25% Health grant them Protection Up (50%) for 2 turns, which can't be dispelled or prevented.
Whenever a Jedi ally gains Foresight, they deal 20% more damage (stacking, max 100%) until the end of battle.
Whenever Jedi Knight Luke uses a Special Ability he gains a Bonus Turn.

While Jedi allies have 100% Health they have 100% Offense, otherwise they have 100% Defense. At the start of their turn, if they are buffed, they gain Advantage for 1 turn, otherwise they gain Tenacity Up for 2 turns.

Whenever Hermit Yoda uses his Basic ability, he reduces his cooldowns by 1 and gains 7% Max Health (stacking, max 210%) for the rest of the encounter. Whenever Hermit Yoda gains a stack of Jedi Lessons, all Jedi allies gain a stack of Jedi Lessons.
